title: 8: I'VE BEEN CHEATED ON. CHEERS TO LEAVING TOXIC PEOPLE IN 2021!
description: A story time EVERYONE needs to hear. Sadie got lied to, completely betrayed, and she's here to tell you it all. Listen in and learn from her mistakes, toxic people aren't worth it, gut feelings are real, and liars will always lie. TO THE NEW YEAR WE GO! Hey Siri, play No Flockin' by Kodak Black.
